11:25.480 --> 11:26.675
He's a very exceptional...

11:26.840 --> 11:29.230
- "Exceptional."
- ...and damaged young man.

11:29.400 --> 11:31.790
- Mm-hm.
- Smart, bright.

11:32.000 --> 11:33.229
He has a chance...

11:33.400 --> 11:37.110
...a future if we keep the police
and the press out of it.

11:39.000 --> 11:41.071
He thinks you can help him.

11:41.760 --> 11:45.151
- You know that's not gonna happen.
- And you can't tell anyone about this.

11:45.320 --> 11:47.471
Not even your wife.

11:48.520 --> 11:51.479
Have your drink, Tom. You earned it.

11:51.640 --> 11:53.313
That water was deep.

11:55.080 --> 11:59.279
I gotta get back to court.
At least look like I'm working.

12:00.040 --> 12:01.713
Think about it.

12:03.240 --> 12:05.232
[###]

