- TOM: So you're back Thursday, then?
- No, no.

13:05.120 --> 13:07.351
I told you,
I'm filling in for Bob this weekend.

13:07.520 --> 13:09.432
- You've been cutting hours...
- I know.

13:09.640 --> 13:10.960
- We could use the cash.
- Sorry.

13:11.120 --> 13:12.554
- You should come.
- This weekend?

13:12.720 --> 13:14.712
- Yeah.
- Is there an opening or something?

13:14.880 --> 13:17.839
- No, it's just...
- I just gotta finish this chapter...

13:18.000 --> 13:19.912
