13:21.960 --> 13:23.838
...a good time.

13:24.480 --> 13:25.994
I got it.

13:26.760 --> 13:28.797
- I hate talking about it this way.
- I get it.

13:28.960 --> 13:32.112
Really, I'm sick of it.
The calendars, the thermometers.

13:32.280 --> 13:34.590
Hey, listen. No, I... I want that.

13:34.760 --> 13:36.353
I do. I want it.

13:37.280 --> 13:40.478
Whatever it takes. As many times as it takes.

13:40.640 --> 13:42.359
- Heh. Okay.
