14:08.080 --> 14:10.515
It's fine.
Just finish whatever you need to finish...

14:10.680 --> 14:12.239
...but try to come down. Okay?

14:12.400 --> 14:14.437
You're beautiful. You know that?

14:30.800 --> 14:32.792
