assume that Nicole lacks conscience.</i>

14:59.720 --> 15:02.599
<i>Many children are obsessed
with issues of loyalty and betrayal.</i>

15:02.760 --> 15:04.240
<i>But hers is a hormone mentality...</i>

15:04.440 --> 15:05.430
[DOORBELL RINGS]

15:05.640 --> 15:06.869
<i>...primitive and exacting.</i>

15:07.040 --> 15:09.077
<i>So the question becomes how to distinguish...</i>

15:09.240 --> 15:12.074
<i>...between access
to a personality disorder...</i>

15:12.240 --> 15:13.594
<i>...and relatively healthy...</i>

15:19.040 --> 15:20.872
[KNOCKING ON DOOR]

15:25.000 --> 15:27.469
Danny, what are you...
What are you doing here?

15:27.640 --> 15:29.552
Hey, I was just in the neighborhood...

15:29.720 --> 15:31.757
...and you left your letter...

15:31.920 --> 15:34.719
...at the hospital the other day.
It has your address on it.

15:35.400 --> 15:37.676
You didn't hear the doorbell? Anyway, um...

15:37.840 --> 15:40.196
It looked important,
like a bill or something.

15:40.360 --> 15:42.750
Oh, well, thank you.

15:43.640 --> 15:45.518
You look a bit better.

15:45.680 --> 15:47.160
How you feeling?

15:47.320 --> 15:50.233
Well, I got out of the hospital,
and I slept like the dead.

15:50.400 --> 15:55.600
Okay. Well, thanks for this,
and I gotta get back to work, so...

15:58.200 --> 15:59.839
What?

16:00.680 --> 16:03.673
You're the only person I can talk to
about what happened.

16:07.720 --> 16:08.756
Can I come in?

16:11.840 --> 16:12.910
- Sure.
- Yeah. Thank you.

16:13.080 --> 16:16.278
Yeah. Of course. I just... Just have a seat.

16:22.600 --> 16:23.750
Look, Danny.

16:23.960 --> 16:25.679
I can give you the name of someone...

16:25.880 --> 16:27.553
...who can help... What are you doing?

16:27.720 --> 16:30.679
What... Please... Please don't smoke in here.

16:31.080 --> 16:33.072
Someone else, huh?

16:33.880 --> 16:35.997
I'm the knife that's been cast into the sea.

16:36.160 --> 16:38.470
- Excuse me?
- Sigmund Freud, doc.

16:38.680 --> 16:40.672
I know. I wouldn't categorize you that way.

16:40.840 --> 16:43.116
Now please put the cigarette out.

16:44.720 --> 16:47.554
- I just want you to know that I really...
- No, Danny, stop.

16:47.720 --> 16:49.552
- We can't. I'm not your therapist.
- Can we talk?

16:49.720 --> 16:52.599
- I'm not your therapist. No.
- I'm sorry.

16:53.160 --> 16:54.879
Jesus.

16:58.240 --> 16:59.799
