my life back on track?

17:11.839 --> 17:13.957
I rendered an opinion.

17:14.119 --> 17:17.954
- That's all.
- You know that I'm innocent.

17:19.040 --> 17:20.440
You gotta know that, right?

17:20.640 --> 17:23.553
