18:10.640 --> 18:11.676
[CHUCKLES]

18:11.960 --> 18:13.394
Really?

18:14.040 --> 18:16.953
Good jab. See you, Louis.

18:26.760 --> 18:29.753
- Hey, Mom.
- ROSE: I'm in here.

18:32.400 --> 18:35.632
- Louis tried to talk to you out there?
- Ah, you could say that. Yeah.

18:35.840 --> 18:37.433
Keeps coming here on his breaks...

18:37.600 --> 18:40.399
