19:05.840 --> 19:08.230
- You sure I can't make you something?
- For goodness sakes.

19:08.400 --> 19:10.392
- I can still take care of myself.
- I know.

19:10.560 --> 19:13.439
- Thank you for getting my groceries.
- Okay.

19:13.600 --> 19:14.954
I love you.

19:15.120 --> 19:17.760
Okay. Okay, buddy. Bye-bye.

19:19.080 --> 19:21.720
