21:55.120 --> 21:58.192
<i>They wanna commit him unless
his parole officer or his therapist...</i>

21:58.360 --> 22:00.238
<i>...comes and gets him.</i>

22:01.040 --> 22:03.396
Okay. I'm not his therapist, so, what...

22:03.560 --> 22:05.597
<i>That's not what he told them.</i>

22:06.400 --> 22:07.959
<i>I can't get over there tonight.</i>

22:08.120 --> 22:10.635
<i>Please help me out on this.</i>

22:10.800 --> 22:12.757
See, you gotta be kidding me.

22:12.920 --> 22:16.470
<i>Tom, like it or not, you're part of this.</i>

22:18.640 --> 22:19.676
